WEBVTT

00:02:30.240 --> 00:02:32.656
But before I do that,
I think it would be important

00:02:32.680 --> 00:02:34.736
to talk a little bit
about the end of life,

00:02:34.760 --> 00:02:37.560
because it forms how I have been
emotionally since then.

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:41.360
Death is such a taboo subject, right?

00:02:42.440 --> 00:02:45.920
Amy ate her last meal on January 9, 2017.

00:02:46.920 --> 00:02:48.976
She somehow lived an additional two months

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:50.240
without solid food.

00:02:51.480 --> 00:02:55.616
Her doctors told us
we could do hospice at home

00:02:55.640 --> 00:02:56.880
or in the hospital.

00:02:57.960 --> 00:03:01.936
They did not tell us that Amy
would shrink to half her body weight,